description:
Born Song Yun Mi, this eccentric and energetic young girl is one of the Borners, surviving test subjects of Snake`s Ua virus experiment. The Ua mutation did not appear to have granted her any extraordinary ability save for an additional appendix; however, her dependence on anti-viral medicine provided by Liang Qi allowed her to be treated as a disposable pawn.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Yunyun
